<http://www.promedmail.org>
[It is interesting this article mentions trypanosomes as a virus and a
vaccination available. As Dr. Reid pointed out in the first piece there are
medications available to treat trypanosome infections. However, to my
knowledge there is no vaccine, nor is this a virus but rather a protozoan.
